works.description: Sirs, this link has to be removed with immediate effect. The news company has already removed the link from their site. It is still cached in your site. The link refers to patented intellectual property that has not yet been sealed, and therefore cannot be disclosed in public until sealed without invalidating our patent. The case in question was a private gearing as it refffered to the patent claims and product, not yet reeased, and must be removed with immediate effect today.
